snippet.textDisplay:
That was fun at the start then I just got so sad. I liked the last girl who cut her hair at the end but the others were really just frenemies or enemies, as I am grinding my teeth at them lol. My youngest sisters 'best' friend used to do her hair when they were still in school. So before they went out every weekend, and sadly my sister didn't realise what was really going on. There was lots of cutting, bleaching and dyeing of her hair and it really got to be a terrible mess. Turns out the girl doing her hair every week was so so jealous of my sisters looks and her sweet personality, because it drew all the boys and the girls to her when they were out at the dances, so she figured she would try to make my sister look as terrible as possible. It was very sad. I found this out a lot later as I was in Canada at the time and my family were in Scotland. She eventually destroyed my sisters hair before another, 'real' friend told her what her amateur hairdresser was really trying to do! I
The hair grew back eventually and she retained her sweet personality... Even met her future husband a couple of years after that! Now Brad your hair is gorgeous in this video. So nice to see you again. I am in Scotland nowadays so I hope your festival goes great and sadly I would not manage this year xxxx
